name: Tall Bandage boots
description:
Bandage Tall boots

Upper Material: Suede 
Insole Material: PVC

special suede leather cleaning instructions: 

Shoes with clean cold water to wet, ensure that the entire shoe was slightly moistened state. Rinse with clean cold water, or wash sponge cleaning agent to remove the product. A small amount of care and cleaning agent solution droplets in a clean wet sponge. Gently scrub and clean all areas. (Classic boots product surface is delicate, such as scrubbing too hard may cause the damage.) Use clean wet sponge to remove excess residue, and then stuffed in the shoes clean paper, in order to shorten the drying time and helps to keep shoe-shaped. Let the boots dry naturally moist for at least 24 hours. Do not bake or direct exposure. After drying, use a soft bristle suede brush suede brush lightly in one direction, making boots reinstated.

*Use wet clean and extremely soft cloth to gently wipe or wiping. 

*Do not rub 

*Do not use any cleaning product 

*Do not use a brush

Processing time: Shiping out within 10 days 
Delivery: 15-45 days
